236
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:04,050
<i>The spell hasn't activated.</i>

237
00:20:04,350 --> 00:20:07,310
<i>Is it possible that he reversed time?</i>

238
00:20:07,890 --> 00:20:11,770
<i>Such a giant space as that?
The entire thing?</i>

239
00:20:17,150 --> 00:20:18,650
<i>Timez Arrow Rain.</i>

240
00:20:21,030 --> 00:20:22,860
<i>Spaces Bout.</i>

241
00:20:38,250 --> 00:20:41,800
Wahlberg. You are strong.

242
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:45,010
But I will become even stronger.

243
00:20:47,810 --> 00:20:53,350
I live only for my own sake.
You cannot surpass me.

244
00:20:53,890 --> 00:20:56,440
I will show you proof right now.

245
00:20:58,520 --> 00:21:01,030
<i>How cruel is fate...</i>

246
00:21:01,940 --> 00:21:06,620
<i>So our ideals are doomed,
never to be realized...</i>

247
00:21:07,370 --> 00:21:10,580
<i>Was the world I envisioned so fragile</i>

248
00:21:10,580 --> 00:21:16,630
<i>that such a small-minded belief
can crush it underfoot?</i>

249
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:20,590
<i>Alas...</i>

250
00:21:21,960 --> 00:21:24,880
Farewell, Wahlberg.

